name: Transdimensional Takedown
description:
This was made for the Clicker jam winter 2023!

"Welcome to the ultimate space adventure - 'Transdimensional Takedown'! In this game, you'll take on the role of a space explorer, venturing through the galaxy in search of valuable resources to collect. Using your trusty clicker, you'll tap and swipe your way through different enemies, collecting money as you go.

As you earn more and more money, you'll be able to upgrade your equipment and purchase helpful tools like autoclickers. These handy devices will automate the clicking process, allowing you to earn even more money while you explore the galaxy.

But be warned, the galaxy is a dangerous place, and you'll need to watch out for hostile alien creatures and treacherous asteroid fields. With each minute you play, the challenges will become greater, but so will the rewards.

Do you have what it takes to become a true Galactic Explorer? Play the game and find out today!"
